"review_level": "None",
"content": "<h2>Examples of embroidery</h2>\n<h3>The entrance curtain to the tabernacle</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:36\">EXO 26:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod27:16\">EXO 27:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:37\">EXO 36:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:18\">EXO 38:18</a></p>\n<h3>Aaron's sash</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:39\">EXO 28:39</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:29\">EXO 39:29</a></p>\n<h3>Costly robes</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:14\">PSA 45:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:10\">EZK 16:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:13\">EZK 16:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:18\">EZK 16:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek26:16\">EZK 26:16</a></p>\n<h3>An expensive sail</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:7\">EZK 27:7</a></p>\n<h2>Embroidery was important in trade</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:16\">EZK 27:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:24\">EZK 27:24</a></p>\n<h2>Embroidered garments were the spoils of war</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:30\">JDG 5:30</a></p>\n<h2>The developing human embryo is likened to God's embroidery</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:15\">PSA 139:15</a></strong></p>",
